@startuml
title Elevator System – Thread Communication Diagram

' ===== Styling =====
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ArrowFontSize 12

' ===== Threads =====
rectangle "networkThread\n(Vetle)" as Network #ADD8E6
rectangle "assignerThread\n(Vetle)" as Assigner #7CFC00
rectangle "fsmThread\n(Lucas)" as FSM #FFDAB9

' ===== Channels / Communication =====

' Filip → Lucas
FSM --> Network : elevalgoServiced\n(elevalgoServiced chan Snapshot)
FSM --> Network : elevalgoLaManana\n(elevalgoLaManana chan Snapshot)

' Lucas → Filip
Network --> FSM : snapshotToFSM\n(snapshotToFSM chan Snapshot)

' Lucas → Vetle
Network --> Assigner : SnapshotOfTheWorld\n(chan Snapshot)

' Vetle → Filip
Assigner --> FSM : assignerOutput\n(chan ElevInput)

@enduml
